{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the first, you know, thing that we saw, we saw the Nazis, the SS, and the SA came in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and this was a very threatening presence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the-- the-- see the SS and the SA were a bunch of hoodlums.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were, you know, the lowest of the lowest to begin with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the SA.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the SS was very ominous in their black uniforms and black boots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- so we were very scared at that point, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the first thing you knew they were making the women clean the swastikas off the streets that they had painted on with toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, Jewish women, they had them clean off the swastikas and clean off the walls and all the slogans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was their first action.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they started the other stuff, beginning to take over Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And eventually, I stopped school then, the-- the-- the middle of the year, because we know there was no sense of continuing anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then-- then it was restricted and you couldn't go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'38.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just of taking over the stores and-- and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as I said, being a threatening presence.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one-- one incident which I-- I should mention.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, as I told you, was in the restaurant supply business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it became more and more difficult for him, and more dangerous for him, because he was not supposed to be doing it anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they prohibited Jews from having stores.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even though he didn't have his store, he-- because he-- what he did, he would buy from the wholesaler and then sell directly himself.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
